the Economics and Technology research group of Boston called Bellclaims that the U.S.andP;  is losing its telecommunications lead &quot;fiction&quot; andaccused the Bells of a &quot;disinformation campaign.&quot;andM;(Dana Blankenhorn/19900406)</TEXT></DOC>